document_data.name: Velsinore
document_data.mainbody: '''Velsinore''' was a senior [[Sel没ne|Sel没nite]] [[priestess]] responsible for the internal administration and accounting of [[Moonshadow Hall]] in the city of [[Yhaunn]]. She turned to be a dangerous heretic and traitor in league with the [[Church of Shar|Sharran]] pirestess [[Variance Amatick]]. She was a follower of the [[Dark Moon heresy]], worshipping both Sel没ne and Shar.
